<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.218156>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Setozius incertus gen. et sp. nov. Holotype male (16.3 × 13.2 mm) (ZRC), left side of carapace denuded. A, overall view; B, frontal view of carapace; C, anterior thoracic sternum and abdomen." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/218156/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.218158>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Setozius incertus gen. et sp. nov. Holotype male (16.3 × 13.2 mm) (ZRC). A, antennules, antennae, epistome and orbits; B, left third maxilliped; C, anterior thoracic sternum; D, male abdomen; E – F, left G 1, abdominal and sternal views; G – H, left G 2, abdominal and sternal views. A – D, setae omitted. Scales: A – D = 2.0 mm; E – H = 1.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/218158/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.218157>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Setozius incertus gen. et sp. nov. Holotype male (16.3 × 13.2 mm) (ZRC). A, outer view of left chela; B, outer view of merus and carpus of cheliped; C, right fourth ambulatory leg." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/218157/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

